ISLAMABAD, Jul 14 (APP): National Command and Operation Center (NCOC) has launched a Complaint Portal in order to address public complains related to vaccination record/certificate issues.
In a Tweet on Tuesday, NCOC asked the citizens to register their complaints by visiting https://t.co/6K7LeAlQ1i https://t.co/HkFHrqpJ3L.
